Author: 55caRtel
Title: [ANN] CZero Mobility
Body: WHITEPAPER | WEBSITE | TELEGRAM | FACEBOOK | TWITTER | YOUTUBE | GITHUB BOUNTY https://i.imgur.com/9W1ds7h.png  Electric Mobility Ecosystem on Blockchain - A $45 Billion Industry  CZERO MOBILITY   CZero Mobility a disruptive startup into the Electric Vehicle Ecosystem space and is now integrating another disruptive technology “Blockchain” into its set of innovative, patented (applied for) solutions.  CZero presents CZERO tokens , the first of its kind ‘Eco Coins’  Based on a globally accepted, incorruptible system of Carbon Credits, CZERO token will be the next carbon credit system for individuals.  Motivating people to leave a greener, better planet for the coming generations.  https://i.imgur.com/a54sMGV.png https://i.imgur.com/NUPxu0i.png https://i.imgur.com/w4sDkvU.png https://i.imgur.com/expgDLB.png  ABOUT CZERO   CZero Electromotives & Ecosystems is a startup based out of India and is a recognized startup by Govt. India and the state province Odisha as well.  CZero is a disruptive startup fully focused on the complete ecosystem around adoption of Electric Mobility and its sustainable future.  Team CZero consists of people having decades of experience in high end technologies, software and business entrepreneurship with education degree from top Indian universities.  Some of the flagship products are cloud connected EV charging station, battery swapping station, wireless charging along with Li-Ion battery.  Fully cloud based backend software that manages every aspects of the product and its usage securely.  https://i.imgur.com/IvJx2eo.png https://i.imgur.com/W3RJG8b.png https://i.imgur.com/Hc93jx1.png https://i.imgur.com/0dh9Ie0.png https://i.imgur.com/ojp2mA7.png AC Level 2 Changing Tower  https://i.imgur.com/rAnM8UP.png  Battery Swapping Station https://i.imgur.com/EJGhg1V.png  Atom: CZero Li IonBattery Modules https://i.imgur.com/d5BxzS1.png  Wireless Changing Pods https://i.imgur.com/kkMfL1b.png  https://i.imgur.com/4RymGE7.png https://i.imgur.com/RHEd1tw.png https://i.imgur.com/qpg1W3s.png  https://i.imgur.com/sISAqBq.png https://i.imgur.com/92erjfW.png https://i.imgur.com/HxxVX2N.png https://i.imgur.com/AQND4LK.png https://i.imgur.com/cc3u82v.png  https://i.imgur.com/jhBFs1T.png https://i.imgur.com/fowBYnd.png https://i.imgur.com/QcvIsL4.png  https://i.imgur.com/KMz8P0L.png https://i.imgur.com/iIj6CqV.png

Author: 55caRtel
Title: [ANN] CZero Mobility
Body: Hi, Apology for the delay. We were setting up everything. Carbon credit today exists at a very high level, such as countries and companies can buy or sell. We are bringing up a carbon credit where every individual can produce, sell, buy. This will be generated from the usage of clean energy based vehicles.
